<!DOCTYPE html><html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Kurd Cafe | Erbil</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cinzel:wght@400;600;700&family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      scroll-behavior: smooth;
    }

    body {
      background: #050505;
      color: #f4d6a0;
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    header {
      min-height: 100vh;
      background: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.8), rgba(0,0,0,0.85)),
      url('logo.jpg') center/cover no-repeat;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .logo {
      width: 280px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.25);
    }

    h1 {
      font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
      font-size: 4rem;
      letter-spacing: 4px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .subtitle {
      color: #d4af37;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    .btn {
      padding: 14px 34px;
      border: 2px solid #d4af37;
      background: transparent;
      color: #d4af37;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 40px;
      transition: 0.3s ease;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .btn:hover {
      background: #d4af37;
      color: black;
      transform: translateY(-3px);
    }

    section {
      padding: 90px 10%;
    }

    .section-title {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 2.7rem;
      font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
      margin-bottom: 60px;
      color: #d4af37;
    }

    .about {
      text-align: center;
      line-height: 1.9;
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: auto;
      color: #ddd;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
    }

    .info-cards {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
      gap: 30px;
      margin-top: 50px;
    }

    .card {
      background: #111;
      padding: 30px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(212,175,55,0.2);
      transition: 0.3s ease;
      box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
    }

    .card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-10px);
      border-color: #d4af37;
    }

    .card h3 {
      color: #d4af37;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      font-size: 1.3rem;
    }

    .card p {
      color: #ccc;
    }

    .menu-gallery {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
      gap: 30px;
    }

    .menu-gallery img {
      width: 100%;
      border-radius: 20px;
      transition: 0.3s ease;
      border: 2px solid rgba(212,175,55,0.15);
    }

    .menu-gallery img:hover {
      transform: scale(1.03);
      border-color: #d4af37;
      box-shadow: 0 0 25px rgba(212,175,55,0.2);
    }

    .hours {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      line-height: 2.2;
      color: #ddd;
    }

    .socials {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 20px;
      margin-top: 30px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .socials a {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #d4af37;
      border: 1px solid #d4af37;
      padding: 12px 22px;
      border-radius: 40px;
      transition: 0.3s;
    }

    .socials a:hover {
      background: #d4af37;
      color: black;
    }

    footer {
      padding: 40px 20px;
      text-align: center;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(212,175,55,0.15);
      color: #aaa;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      background: #080808;
    }

    @media(max-width:768px) {
      h1 {
        font-size: 2.8rem;
      }

      .logo {
        width: 220px;
      }

      .section-title {
        font-size: 2rem;
      }
    }
  </style></head>
<body>  <header>
    <img src="logo.jpg" alt="Kurd Cafe Logo" class="logo">
    <h1>KURD CAFE</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">Luxury Coffee Experience • Erbil</p>
    <a href="#menu" class="btn">View Menu</a>
  </header>  <section>
    <h2 class="section-title">About Kurd Cafe</h2>
    <div class="about">
      Welcome to Kurd Cafe — a modern luxury cafe experience inspired by the beauty of Erbil. 
      Enjoy premium coffee, refreshing juices, desserts, and a relaxing atmosphere with elegant black and gold aesthetics.
    </div><div class="info-cards">
  <div class="card">
    <h3>Opening Hours</h3>
    <p>Every Day</p>
    <p>6:00 AM — 11:00 PM</p>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h3>Location</h3>
    <p>Coming Soon</p>
    <p>Erbil, Kurdistan</p>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h3>Contact</h3>
    <p>Phone Number Coming Soon</p>
  </div>
</div>

  </section>  <section id="menu">
    <h2 class="section-title">Our Menu</h2><div class="menu-gallery">
  <img src="menu1.jpg" alt="Coffee Menu">
  <img src="menu2.jpg" alt="Dessert Menu">
</div>

  </section>  <section>
    <h2 class="section-title">Opening Hours</h2><div class="hours">
  Monday — Sunday <br>
  6:00 AM — 11:00 PM
</div>

<div class="socials">
  <a href="#">Instagram</a>
  <a href="#">TikTok</a>
  <a href="#">Facebook</a>
</div>

  </section>  <footer>
    © 2026 Kurd Cafe — All Rights Reserved.
  </footer></body>
</html>